{"tid":2102324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國情報部門：消費者予中國支付公司個人資料會落入北京手上","createTime":"2020-07-10T11:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T11:41:13.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"478e0f9a46de89d27d61a42ed7cecd0da72cb520","tid":2102324,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"德國情報部門：消費者予中國支付公司個人資料會落入北京手上<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=397438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397438&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumv%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=eaa94db8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397438&h=f4cf59b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=397438</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】德國情報部門警告，當地消費者提供予中國支付及科技公司的個人資料，會落入中國政府手中。<br />\n<br />\n德國情報部門發表的年度報告指，中國官員可以獲取包括阿里巴巴和騰訊等中國公司，儲存在中國的德國消費者個人資料，而其他在德國營運的中國應用程式、網絡服務以及手機供應商等，他們獲取的消費者資料，中方官員亦同樣可以取得。<br />\n<br />\n情報部門警告，由於中國的公司需要按中國法律，向北京政府提交相關資料，德國消費者個人資料被濫用不足為奇。<br />\n<br />\n有情報官員又表示，關注來自中國的混合威脅，包括來自中國的資金，購買德國重要的公司和企業。<br />\n<br />\n另外，德國內政部長表示，當局仍未決定是否容許中國電訊設備商華為，參與當地的5G網絡建設。"},{"pid":"2c19689bd07d5991d171f7c9283c08d9c2c1c39e","tid":2102324,"uid":151074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:27:31.000Z","msg":"德國肥婆已犯国安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56fb38ed4840d2418ce4d86589abcf1a21150177","tid":2102324,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f375bee3a7004b2c6a71a3f10196c9d4bea15312","tid":2102324,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:29:53.000Z","msg":"共享私隱<img src=\"/